                        <span class="faq-icon">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We'll always give you honest advice. Generally, repair if the appliance is less than 8 years old and the repair costs less than 50% of replacement. Replace if it's over 15 years old, needs frequent repairs, or is energy-inefficient. We'll help you make the most cost-effective decision.</p>
